1
00:00:32,291 --> 00:00:36,125
[KAYO'S MOM] Kayo! If you
don't hurry, you'll be late!

2
00:00:36,208 --> 00:00:38,458
Coming! Sorry for the wait!

3
00:00:38,541 --> 00:00:40,833
Wow! You look like a
real-deal high schooler!

4
00:00:40,916 --> 00:00:41,750
[KAYO]
I know, right?

5
00:00:41,833 --> 00:00:42,958
You have everything?

6
00:00:43,041 --> 00:00:44,208
[KAYO]
I think so.

7
00:00:44,291 --> 00:00:46,375
Well, let's go!

8
00:00:46,458 --> 00:00:48,791
[PRINCIPAL 3A] And now,
as you take your first steps

9
00:00:48,875 --> 00:00:50,625
on a new path in your lives...

10
00:00:50,708 --> 00:00:54,583
[bell rings]

11
00:00:54,666 --> 00:00:55,958
[door opens]

12
00:00:56,041 --> 00:00:59,208
[FEMALE TEACHER 3A]
Okay, everyone. Take your seats.

13
00:02:34,041 --> 00:02:40,833
[beeping]

14
00:02:46,500 --> 00:02:49,125
[coughing]

15
00:03:08,916 --> 00:03:10,791
[coughs]

16
00:03:22,833 --> 00:03:25,291
So, uh.

17
00:03:25,375 --> 00:03:28,208
You must be the one who's been
taking care of this little guy.

18
00:03:28,291 --> 00:03:31,916
Oh. Yes. I guess I have been.

19
00:03:35,833 --> 00:03:38,083
[coughing]

20
00:03:38,166 --> 00:03:40,666
Um, you all right?

21
00:03:40,750 --> 00:03:42,333
[KAYO]
I'm fi-- [coughs]

22
00:03:42,416 --> 00:03:43,708
[HARUTO]
You sure?

23
00:03:43,791 --> 00:03:46,250
[KAYO]
I'm okay. Thank you.

24
00:03:46,333 --> 00:03:48,333
Please excuse me!

25
00:03:50,125 --> 00:03:53,083
[panting]

26
00:03:53,166 --> 00:03:55,083
[KAYO]
That came out of nowhere.

27
00:03:55,166 --> 00:03:57,125
I wonder what that was?

28
00:03:57,208 --> 00:04:01,208
It's been a long time since
I talked to anyone.

29
00:04:13,833 --> 00:04:17,750
A park, huh?

30
00:04:17,833 --> 00:04:20,458
I wonder whose dream this is?

31
00:04:26,458 --> 00:04:28,250
[coughs]

32
00:04:31,791 --> 00:04:32,583
Go after her.

33
00:04:32,666 --> 00:04:33,583
What are you talking about?

34
00:04:33,666 --> 00:04:35,041
Hurry up and go!

35
00:04:35,125 --> 00:04:40,041
[HARUTO] What? Great.
Back where I started.

36
00:04:40,125 --> 00:04:41,875
So, what am I s'posed
to talk about?

37
00:04:41,958 --> 00:04:44,083
I'll leave that up to you.

38
00:04:51,083 --> 00:04:52,666
[LILY grunts]

39
00:04:52,750 --> 00:04:53,541
So, uh.

40
00:04:53,625 --> 00:04:54,416
[KAYO]
Uh!

41
00:04:54,500 --> 00:04:55,625
[HARUTO]
You must be the one

42
00:04:55,708 --> 00:04:57,416
who's been taking care
of this little guy.

43
00:04:57,500 --> 00:04:59,583
[KAYO]
Oh. Yes.

44
00:05:01,333 --> 00:05:03,833
[MALE STUDENT 3A]
Teacher! It's Sugisaki.

45
00:05:03,916 --> 00:05:04,750
[FEMALE TEACHER 3A]
What's wrong?

46
00:05:04,833 --> 00:05:06,166
[MALE STUDENT 3B]
Are you--

47
00:05:06,250 --> 00:05:07,375
[KAYO'S MOM]
Kayo!

48
00:05:07,458 --> 00:05:12,583
[gasps, panting]

49
00:05:15,583 --> 00:05:17,041
[gasps]

50
00:05:24,708 --> 00:05:26,250
Hello.

51
00:05:28,125 --> 00:05:31,583
Jeez. I was good enough
until she showed up, huh?

52
00:05:31,666 --> 00:05:33,833
I guess you must more
of a lady's man.

53
00:05:33,916 --> 00:05:38,041
Uh. No, wait. It's this.

54
00:05:39,291 --> 00:05:40,250
[meows]

55
00:05:40,333 --> 00:05:42,750
Who's a crafty little kitty?

56
00:05:42,833 --> 00:05:44,250
[KAYO laughs]

57
00:05:46,250 --> 00:05:48,041
[yawns]

58
00:05:49,333 --> 00:05:50,458
[KAYO coughs]

59
00:05:50,541 --> 00:05:52,375
Oh. Have a cold?

60
00:05:52,458 --> 00:05:57,375
I've just been feeling a little
under the weather lately.

61
00:05:57,458 --> 00:05:59,333
But still though,
it must be hard

62
00:05:59,416 --> 00:06:01,125
taking care of him every day.

63
00:06:01,208 --> 00:06:03,750
Well, my house is
actually nearby,

64
00:06:03,833 --> 00:06:06,208
and I wanted to see Potato Chip.

65
00:06:06,291 --> 00:06:11,458
I don't have a lot of stamina,
so I can't really go very far.

66
00:06:11,541 --> 00:06:13,375
I see.

67
00:06:13,458 --> 00:06:17,250
But there's gotta be
some place you wanna go.

68
00:06:17,333 --> 00:06:19,916
Somewhere I want to go?

69
00:06:29,333 --> 00:06:30,500
I don't know.

70
00:06:30,583 --> 00:06:32,833
Nothing comes to mind.

71
00:06:36,416 --> 00:06:38,458
And what if I offered
to take you somewhere?

72
00:06:38,541 --> 00:06:40,000
Huh?

73
00:06:40,083 --> 00:06:42,708
Look, you don't have to come
with me if you don't want to.

74
00:06:42,791 --> 00:06:44,208
I...

75
00:06:46,125 --> 00:06:47,708
[HARUTO]
How's this?

76
00:06:47,791 --> 00:06:49,666
I will be here at
10 o'clock tomorrow.

77
00:06:49,750 --> 00:06:51,833
Just come by if you wanna go.

78
00:06:51,916 --> 00:06:52,791
Bye.

79
00:06:52,875 --> 00:06:54,541
[KAYO]
Uh...

80
00:06:57,291 --> 00:06:59,375
What now?

81
00:06:59,458 --> 00:07:02,458
Is it really okay
to go with him?

82
00:07:02,541 --> 00:07:03,541
[meows]

83
00:07:03,625 --> 00:07:04,833
[gasps]

84
00:07:13,791 --> 00:07:15,166
[HARUTO]
Morning.

85
00:07:15,250 --> 00:07:16,333
Were you waiting long?

86
00:07:16,416 --> 00:07:18,041
[KAYO]
No. Not at all.

87
00:07:18,125 --> 00:07:22,208
Glad to hear that.
So, shall we head out?

88
00:07:22,291 --> 00:07:23,416
[gasps]

89
00:07:24,833 --> 00:07:26,791
[HARUTO] You don't need much
stamina to ride that!

90
00:07:39,208 --> 00:07:40,583
[laughs]

91
00:08:05,333 --> 00:08:10,500
[HARUTO, KAYO laughing]

92
00:08:19,458 --> 00:08:21,916
[HARUTO]
Well, take care heading home.

93
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:24,750
[KAYO]
I will. Thanks again for today!

94
00:08:24,833 --> 00:08:26,625
You be careful
heading home, too!

95
00:08:26,708 --> 00:08:28,083
[HARUTO]
Yeah.

96
00:08:31,208 --> 00:08:32,458
She needs help.

97
00:08:32,541 --> 00:08:34,875
[HARUTO]
You again?

98
00:08:34,958 --> 00:08:36,208
What?

99
00:08:38,625 --> 00:08:40,291
[phone chimes]

100
00:09:28,041 --> 00:09:31,083
[KAYO]
He isn't here yet.

101
00:09:31,166 --> 00:09:33,208
I hope he comes soon.

102
00:09:34,041 --> 00:09:35,500
[gasps]

103
00:09:35,583 --> 00:09:38,541
[KAYO]
Just now. I-I...

104
00:09:41,666 --> 00:09:44,958
[KAYO]
Do I... like Haruto?

105
00:09:45,041 --> 00:09:50,333
[heartbeats]

106
00:09:50,416 --> 00:09:51,708
[KAYO gasps]

107
00:09:54,291 --> 00:09:55,916
[KAYO grunts]

108
00:09:58,625 --> 00:10:02,083
[KAYO]
Oh. Again.

109
00:10:06,208 --> 00:10:08,125
Kayo!

110
00:10:08,208 --> 00:10:10,291
[KAYO]
Haruto...

111
00:10:13,791 --> 00:10:18,000
[KAYO]
Why is it always me?

112
00:10:18,083 --> 00:10:19,458
It isn't fair!

113
00:10:19,541 --> 00:10:22,916
[HARUTO gasping]

114
00:10:43,458 --> 00:10:44,958
[HARUTO]
Wait...

115
00:10:47,083 --> 00:10:48,375
[LILY]
Brother.

116
00:10:48,458 --> 00:10:49,833
What?

117
00:10:49,916 --> 00:10:51,291
She's already.

118
00:10:51,375 --> 00:10:52,875
She's...

119
00:10:52,958 --> 00:10:55,625
She's what, already?

120
00:10:55,708 --> 00:10:59,000
It might be too late.

121
00:11:00,666 --> 00:11:03,250
[LILY]
She's started to become a witch.

122
00:11:09,458 --> 00:11:10,958
[gasps]

123
00:11:13,041 --> 00:11:17,083
[beeping]

124
00:11:22,458 --> 00:11:23,583
[gasps]

125
00:11:26,708 --> 00:11:28,500
[coughs]

126
00:11:28,583 --> 00:11:31,541
[STUDENTS chattering]

127
00:11:32,333 --> 00:11:35,041
[coughing]

128
00:11:37,666 --> 00:11:42,458
[KAYO]
Why... is it always me?

129
00:11:42,541 --> 00:11:43,708
Why?

130
00:11:43,791 --> 00:11:46,000
[HARUTO]
Kayo!

131
00:11:56,583 --> 00:11:58,916
[HARUTO whimpering]

132
00:12:06,333 --> 00:12:09,250
[HARUTO]
Kayo, I...

133
00:12:09,333 --> 00:12:14,250
Haruto. I feel so different.

134
00:12:14,333 --> 00:12:17,250
It's like I've been reborn.

135
00:12:17,333 --> 00:12:19,875
Oh. Right.

136
00:12:22,416 --> 00:12:26,333
Is what Lily said to me
about her true, you think?

137
00:12:26,416 --> 00:12:29,083
The witch's power seems
to be at play temporarily,

138
00:12:29,166 --> 00:12:30,791
at the very least.

139
00:12:30,875 --> 00:12:35,083
But she doesn't have long
before shuffling off.

140
00:12:36,125 --> 00:12:38,083
[rustling]

141
00:12:46,333 --> 00:12:50,000
[HARUTO] So, where do you
think we should go today?

142
00:12:50,083 --> 00:12:52,250
Oh, thanks, but...

143
00:12:52,333 --> 00:12:53,250
[HARUTO]
Hm?

144
00:12:53,333 --> 00:12:55,625
I wanna walk today.

145
00:13:19,750 --> 00:13:23,375
[KAYO laughing]

146
00:13:31,833 --> 00:13:33,750
[HARUTO]
It's a school.

147
00:13:37,541 --> 00:13:39,208
[HARUTO]
Did you go here?

148
00:13:57,416 --> 00:13:59,916
[HARUTO]
What class were you in?

149
00:14:02,708 --> 00:14:06,250
[HARUTO] You don't really
like school, do you?

150
00:14:06,333 --> 00:14:09,041
[KAYO]
Class Three.

151
00:14:09,125 --> 00:14:12,083
First year. Class Three.

152
00:14:15,250 --> 00:14:18,916
[HARUTO]
Whoa, this really takes me back!

153
00:14:25,333 --> 00:14:28,208
Uh. Huh?

154
00:14:28,291 --> 00:14:30,625
It's just...

155
00:14:30,708 --> 00:14:32,500
Sorry.

156
00:14:33,833 --> 00:14:35,625
[rattling]

157
00:14:42,875 --> 00:14:45,416
[fireworks popping]

158
00:14:45,500 --> 00:14:46,916
[gasps]

159
00:14:47,875 --> 00:14:49,833
Whoa.

160
00:14:53,875 --> 00:14:56,625
[CROWD chattering]

161
00:14:56,708 --> 00:15:01,041
[gasping]

162
00:15:04,375 --> 00:15:06,083
The Festival!

163
00:15:06,166 --> 00:15:08,458
I finally got to go!

164
00:15:10,333 --> 00:15:13,458
[KAYO laughs]
That was so much fun! Hey!

165
00:15:13,541 --> 00:15:15,500
[HARUTO]
Wow, it's after seven?

166
00:15:15,583 --> 00:15:18,291
Since it's already dark,
I'll walk you home this time.

167
00:15:18,375 --> 00:15:21,375
Uh. Okay.

168
00:15:25,125 --> 00:15:27,208
What should we do tomorrow?

169
00:15:31,875 --> 00:15:34,875
Are you okay?

170
00:15:34,958 --> 00:15:36,250
--Kayo?
--[gasps]

171
00:15:36,333 --> 00:15:37,291
Are you getting tired?

172
00:15:37,375 --> 00:15:40,916
Oh! I'm fine, but thanks.

173
00:15:41,416 --> 00:15:43,166
[HARUTO]
Well. I'll see ya tomorrow.

174
00:15:43,250 --> 00:15:45,833
Okay. Bye.

175
00:15:55,333 --> 00:15:57,083
[HARUTO]
Hey.

176
00:15:59,208 --> 00:16:00,166
What's up?

177
00:16:00,250 --> 00:16:02,208
[panting]

178
00:16:02,291 --> 00:16:04,083
Yo, Kayo?

179
00:16:05,458 --> 00:16:06,875
Forehead's hot.

180
00:16:06,958 --> 00:16:09,166
Did this start on the walk home?

181
00:16:11,375 --> 00:16:12,541
Why didn'tcha say
something sooner?

182
00:16:12,625 --> 00:16:14,250
[KAYO]
Wait! That's not...

183
00:16:14,333 --> 00:16:17,541
I... I'm sorry!

184
00:16:17,625 --> 00:16:19,125
--[KAYO gasps]
--[crash]

185
00:16:19,208 --> 00:16:20,708
[HARUTO]
Kayo!

186
00:16:22,125 --> 00:16:23,625
Take it easy, you shouldn't
push yourself--

187
00:16:23,708 --> 00:16:26,541
I told you that wasn't it!

188
00:16:26,625 --> 00:16:30,166
[KAYO laughing]

189
00:16:30,250 --> 00:16:31,791
Huh...?

190
00:16:38,083 --> 00:16:41,208
[KAYO] I wish I didn't
have to go home already.

191
00:16:45,833 --> 00:16:49,666
[KAYO]
I wonder... What are we doing?

192
00:16:49,750 --> 00:16:54,625
I mean, does this count
as a date, or not?

193
00:16:54,708 --> 00:16:56,750
Now that I think about it,

194
00:16:56,833 --> 00:17:00,708
no one else has ever walked
me all the way home before.

195
00:17:04,291 --> 00:17:06,791
[KAYO]
Hm? Wait.

196
00:17:06,875 --> 00:17:09,250
If he escorts me
all the way home,

197
00:17:09,333 --> 00:17:12,625
normally, we'd say "good
night" outside my door.

198
00:17:12,708 --> 00:17:14,625
And after that--

199
00:17:14,708 --> 00:17:16,291
[heartbeats]

200
00:17:16,375 --> 00:17:18,083
[KAYO]
K-Kiss?

201
00:17:18,166 --> 00:17:19,291
[HARUTO]
What should we do tomorrow?

202
00:17:19,375 --> 00:17:21,750
[KAYO]
Will we? In just a minute.

203
00:17:21,833 --> 00:17:25,333
But, we're not like,
actually dating yet.

204
00:17:25,416 --> 00:17:26,166
Kayo?

205
00:17:26,250 --> 00:17:27,000
[gasps]

206
00:17:27,083 --> 00:17:27,916
Are you getting tired?

207
00:17:28,000 --> 00:17:31,916
Oh! I'm fine, but thanks.

208
00:17:32,000 --> 00:17:36,083
[KAYO] What should I do?
We're almost home!

209
00:17:37,625 --> 00:17:39,583
[HARUTO]
Well. I'll see ya tomorrow.

210
00:17:39,666 --> 00:17:43,000
[KAYO]
I can't do this right now!

211
00:17:46,625 --> 00:17:52,125
[panting]

212
00:17:56,875 --> 00:18:00,708
[KAYO] Haruto. How do
you feel about me?

213
00:18:00,791 --> 00:18:03,958
Do you like me?

214
00:18:04,041 --> 00:18:06,375
Because I think I...

215
00:18:09,708 --> 00:18:11,166
[door slams]

216
00:18:14,166 --> 00:18:15,541
[grunts]

217
00:18:18,250 --> 00:18:20,125
All right.

218
00:18:24,083 --> 00:18:25,791
[HARUTO]
Hey.

219
00:18:26,458 --> 00:18:29,541
[KAYO]
He... He's here!

220
00:18:29,625 --> 00:18:32,666
[panting]

221
00:18:32,750 --> 00:18:34,666
What's up? [gasps]

222
00:18:34,750 --> 00:18:35,916
Yo, Kayo?

223
00:18:36,000 --> 00:18:38,500
[gasping]

224
00:18:38,583 --> 00:18:40,250
[HARUTO]
Forehead's hot.

225
00:18:40,333 --> 00:18:42,333
Did this start on the walk home?

226
00:18:42,416 --> 00:18:44,208
[KAYO]
This is hard.

227
00:18:44,291 --> 00:18:45,291
[HARUTO] Why didn'tcha
say something sooner?

228
00:18:45,375 --> 00:18:48,708
Wait! That's not...

229
00:18:48,791 --> 00:18:50,458
I... I'm sorry!

230
00:18:50,541 --> 00:18:51,833
--[KAYO grunts]
--[crash]

231
00:18:51,916 --> 00:18:52,875
Kayo!

232
00:18:54,416 --> 00:18:55,625
Take it easy,
you shouldn't push yourself--

233
00:18:55,708 --> 00:18:57,125
I told you that wasn't it!

234
00:18:57,208 --> 00:18:58,833
Huh?

235
00:18:58,916 --> 00:19:02,625
[KAYO laughs]

236
00:19:02,708 --> 00:19:04,250
Huh...?

237
00:19:08,625 --> 00:19:12,583
Sorry. But I really am
feeling fine, thanks.

238
00:19:14,291 --> 00:19:20,583
Actually. I have something that
I really needed to give to you.

239
00:19:20,666 --> 00:19:22,291
Here.

240
00:19:22,375 --> 00:19:23,583
[HARUTO]
Uh.

241
00:19:28,208 --> 00:19:30,333
[gasping]

242
00:19:31,916 --> 00:19:34,666
[beeping]

243
00:19:39,291 --> 00:19:42,375
[KAYO]
No. Where'd it go?

244
00:19:44,125 --> 00:19:45,541
Kayo.

245
00:19:45,625 --> 00:19:46,791
[KAYO]
I still...

246
00:19:46,875 --> 00:19:49,666
I haven't told him.

247
00:19:49,750 --> 00:19:52,041
I can't leave things like this.

248
00:19:52,125 --> 00:19:53,750
I won't!

249
00:19:58,083 --> 00:19:59,541
[KAYO]
Thank you.

250
00:19:59,625 --> 00:20:02,291
I, uh... I'm fine.

251
00:20:04,041 --> 00:20:08,541
I had a letter to give you,
but I, I lost it.

252
00:20:08,625 --> 00:20:13,125
I wrote it, because I really
wanted to tell you at the end.

253
00:20:13,208 --> 00:20:15,583
What do you mean?

254
00:20:15,666 --> 00:20:18,958
I, uh, heard you two talk.

255
00:20:19,041 --> 00:20:21,250
You and your friend.

256
00:20:23,791 --> 00:20:28,083
But you know, when I got
to spend time with you,

257
00:20:28,166 --> 00:20:30,416
I thought "this is
what it must be like

258
00:20:30,500 --> 00:20:32,333
to have a normal
high school life."

259
00:20:32,416 --> 00:20:33,833
Like...

260
00:20:33,916 --> 00:20:37,833
Like, "this must be what it's
like to have a boyfriend."

261
00:20:37,916 --> 00:20:41,041
And those thoughts were nice.

262
00:20:41,125 --> 00:20:45,250
And after it all, I wish...

263
00:20:45,333 --> 00:20:48,041
I didn't have to leave.

264
00:20:48,125 --> 00:20:48,916
But...

265
00:20:49,000 --> 00:20:49,958
[gasps]

266
00:20:50,041 --> 00:20:53,708
[KAYO]
It looks like my time is up.

267
00:20:53,791 --> 00:20:56,250
Thank you, Haruto.

268
00:20:56,333 --> 00:21:00,208
You made me... feel joyful.

269
00:21:00,291 --> 00:21:02,791
I've never been happier!

270
00:21:14,708 --> 00:21:16,541
I love you.

271
00:21:16,625 --> 00:21:19,291
I hope you'll remember that.

272
00:21:23,250 --> 00:21:25,416
Keep me in your heart.

273
00:21:43,666 --> 00:21:47,416
[HARUTO cries]

274
00:23:46,333 --> 00:23:48,875
[LILY] When you get hunger pains
in the middle of the night,

275
00:23:48,958 --> 00:23:51,458
do you find something
to snack on, too?

276
00:23:51,541 --> 00:23:54,250
[EGOS]
Yes I do, baa.

277
00:23:54,333 --> 00:23:58,083
[LILY] Next time's dream is:
"The Witch of Gluttony."

